(Monies, 1879)
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="87463686B03B8805FF42FCFB9BDC7786" blockId="5.[174,1232,655,970]" pageId="5" pageNumber="476">Hosts: American bison (P = 18.2 %; I = 2 (1–3)); banteng (P = 100 %; I = 1); gayal (P = 100 %; I = 3).</paragraph>
